  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3558720/extras/74d10eae303a6d048d714bd9c2091031.poster.avif?t=1749030384\" width=800 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3558720/extras/74d10eae303a6d048d714bd9c2091031.webm?t=1749030384\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sophie is blind, alone, and lost in a crumbling mansion. Her only hope? You, her beloved teddy bear. In Out of Sight VR, you’ll see the world through Teddy’s eyes and guide Sophie, navigating a world of creeping shadows and haunting secrets.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3558720/extras/fb217c68555be5bc06b23a923e373dc5.poster.avif?t=1749030384\" width=800 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3558720/extras/fb217c68555be5bc06b23a923e373dc5.webm?t=1749030384\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Flip the perspective and take control in a genre-defying second-person VR experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This groundbreaking second-person VR horror flips the script on traditional perspective. As Teddy, you’re Sophie’s only friend - and only lifeline. Strategically position yourself to scout dangers, uncover hidden paths, and lead Sophie away from the sinister figures hunting her every move.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3558720/extras/d447a5226c41b4080c907691421aad16.poster.avif?t=1749030384\" width=800 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3558720/extras/d447a5226c41b4080c907691421aad16.webm?t=1749030384\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tension hangs on every breath, and each movement must be planned with care. One wrong step, one creak of the floorboards, and Sophie could be caught.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face perspective-shifting chase sequences, solve second-perspective puzzles, and uncover the tragic history buried within the mansion’s walls. As fear builds and reality fractures, the line between protector and prisoner begins to blur.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3558720/extras/be408b59a981f7648da3c1cd91fbac41.poster.avif?t=1749030384\" width=800 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3558720/extras/be408b59a981f7648da3c1cd91fbac41.webm?t=1749030384\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover the haunting past hidden inside the walls and within Sophie herself.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dripping with atmosphere and driven by emotional stakes, Out of Sight VR is more than your standard horror game. Every choice you make as Teddy could mean survival...or silence.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3558720/extras/a0e27e3489f6751d35d6efd56ce11e55.poster.avif?t=1749030384\" width=800 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3558720/extras/a0e27e3489f6751d35d6efd56ce11e55.webm?t=1749030384\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></h2>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3558720/extras/74d10eae303a6d048d714bd9c2091031.poster.avif?t=1749030384\" width=800 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3558720/extras/74d10eae303a6d048d714bd9c2091031.webm?t=1749030384\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sophie is blind, alone, and lost in a crumbling mansion. Her only hope? You, her beloved teddy bear. In Out of Sight VR, you’ll see the world through Teddy’s eyes and guide Sophie, navigating a world of creeping shadows and haunting secrets.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3558720/extras/fb217c68555be5bc06b23a923e373dc5.poster.avif?t=1749030384\" width=800 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3558720/extras/fb217c68555be5bc06b23a923e373dc5.webm?t=1749030384\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Flip the perspective and take control in a genre-defying second-person VR experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This groundbreaking second-person VR horror flips the script on traditional perspective. As Teddy, you’re Sophie’s only friend - and only lifeline. Strategically position yourself to scout dangers, uncover hidden paths, and lead Sophie away from the sinister figures hunting her every move.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3558720/extras/d447a5226c41b4080c907691421aad16.poster.avif?t=1749030384\" width=800 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3558720/extras/d447a5226c41b4080c907691421aad16.webm?t=1749030384\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tension hangs on every breath, and each movement must be planned with care. One wrong step, one creak of the floorboards, and Sophie could be caught.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face perspective-shifting chase sequences, solve second-perspective puzzles, and uncover the tragic history buried within the mansion’s walls. As fear builds and reality fractures, the line between protector and prisoner begins to blur.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3558720/extras/be408b59a981f7648da3c1cd91fbac41.poster.avif?t=1749030384\" width=800 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3558720/extras/be408b59a981f7648da3c1cd91fbac41.webm?t=1749030384\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover the haunting past hidden inside the walls and within Sophie herself.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dripping with atmosphere and driven by emotional stakes, Out of Sight VR is more than your standard horror game. Every choice you make as Teddy could mean survival...or silence.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3558720/extras/a0e27e3489f6751d35d6efd56ce11e55.poster.avif?t=1749030384\" width=800 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3558720/extras/a0e27e3489f6751d35d6efd56ce11e55.webm?t=1749030384\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></h2>",
